# SafeScan

## Android Security Monitoring Application

SafeScan is a mobile security application designed to monitor suspicious runtime behaviors on Android devices and help users identify potentially malicious applications in real time.

The application combines Android system-level APIs, background monitoring services, and cloud-based data storage to provide runtime threat analysis and security alerts for users.

---

# Features

- Real-time application behavior monitoring
- Suspicious activity detection and logging
- Malware report and threat tracking database
- Background monitoring services
- Security alert notifications
- User authentication and cloud synchronization
- Application risk visualization interface

---

